Nemesis Enforcer/Scattershot/Ares:




Nemesis Enforcer, Scattershot, and Ares stepped out of the CR room, good as 
new.

"Blasted Mafia.  They probably died already, and we won't get any revenge!" 
Nemesis yelled.

"Death Storm says there are still some left." Scattershot replied, referring 
to his helmet, the ex-Alliance member Death Storm's head.  

After hearing the call for battle, the three bots ran for the nearest exit, 
eager to kick tailgate.
